Although, I really suppport this goal, I don't believe we are there yet. 
The webui still uses a lot of the Rest D-Bus interfaces, as does the test suite, and the current Redfish API is still missing things like SNMP (in 2019.3 but not implemented in bmcweb, IBM has someone working on this), resolved event log field (should be in the 2020.1 spec), TPMEnable (need to get into Redfish), LastRebootTime (maybe we drop from the webui), LastStateChangeTime (maybe we drop from the webui), RemoteLoggingServer (in the spec but not implemented in bmcweb)
